This Converter converts URLs to mp3 files. ONLY FOR PERSONAL USE!

Dependencies:
You need to install:
    - FFMPEG
    - yt-dlp
    - yt-dlp-ejs
    - external java script runtime (The script was tested on Deno)

    More information on following sites:
    https://github.com/yt-dlp/ejs
    https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp
    https://github.com/denoland/deno
    https://ffmpeg.org/




HOW TO USE:
1. Change the output_dir
2. Change the path from ffmpeg_location and ffprobe_location
3. Run the code and copy URLs into
4. Check the output_dir
